  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0dad\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dad\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Four others who attacked MP's houses are arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Senior Superintendent of Police lawyer Mr. Nihal Talduwa said that 4 persons have been arrested after attacking the house of Member of Parliament Taraka Balasuriya and the house of Member of Parliament Geetha Kumarasinghe as well as the National Television and a cab of Thavalama local council.",
        "The Kegalle division investigating officers have arrested a person in Kegalle area for attacking the house of Member of Parliament Taraka Balasuriya on Bandaranayake Mawatha, Kegalle on May 9, and Welikada Maligawa Road for breaking into the house of Mrs. Geetha Kumarasinghe on Rajagiriya Nawala Road and damaging the property. A person has been arrested in the area by the Welikada Police Station.",
        "The spokesperson said that a person was arrested in Pelawatta area by Thalangama police for attacking and damaging a cab belonging to Thawalama local council on May 1st on the road in front of Thawalama post 8.",
        "In addition, on July 13, a man from Moratuwa area was handed over to the Kurunduwatta police for entering the National Television Corporation, intimidating the employees and causing damage to government property.",
        "The arrested suspects are 22, 46, 48, and 51 years old and are residents of Kegalle, Meepitiya, Rajagiriya, Moratuwa and Entre Kotte."
      ],
